	"stageBrief": "Welcome to stage <some cool name>. My name is <your name> and I am the CRO for this stage.\r\n\r\n<some cool name> is a 30 round, 150 point Standard <stage-size> course. There are 14 <metric/classic> targets and 2 steel. The start signal is audible.\r\n\r\nThe start position is standing anywhere in the shooting area, facing down range with wrists below belt. Handgun is loaded and holstered.\r\nPCC start position is standing anywhere in the shooting area, facing down range, stock on belt, safety on, muzzle pointed down range, loaded carbine held in both hands with safety on.\r\n\r\nOn the audible start signal, engage all targets from within the shooting area. Best two hits on paper and steel must fall to score.",
